Hi Dennis,

I mounted a HANG-ON!!! strap from a passenger bus on the inside of my 
slider. It uses one of the existing bolts and I drilled a hole for a 
short sheet-metal screw. I've used it at least three times and it 
hasn't snapped off yet!

http://www.pottsfamily.ca/westfakia/doorstrap.jpg

